<%- content_for :title, "Flash Messages" -%>

<%- content_for :above_layout do -%>
  <%= render "shared/flash", flash: { "alert" => "Example alert message" } -%>
  <%= render "shared/flash", flash: { "error" => "Example error message" } -%>
  <%= render "shared/flash", flash: { "notice" => "Example notice message" } -%>
  <%= render "shared/flash", flash: { "success" => "Example success message" } -%>
<%- end -%>

<div class="content-spacing">
  <p>Here you can see an example flash message.</p>
  <p>Flash messages use the panel styling and go full-width by default.</p>
  <p>The flash message by default sits just below the <code>above_layout</code> yield.</p>
</div>